                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div> Share
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>11 May 1950</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 475</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">
<div class="content-item" id="contribution-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Attlee)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">With your permission, Mr. Speaker, I would like to make a short statement with regard to the French Government's proposals for the integration of French and German coal and steel production, in which I am sure the House is very much interested.<p></p> It is the declared policy of the Western Powers to promote the entry of Germany as a free member into the comity of European nations. The French proposals are designed to facilitate that process and must consequently be regarded as a notable contribution towards the solution of a major European problem.<p></p> The proposals also have far-reaching implications for the future economic structure of participating countries; and this aspect will require very careful study by His Majesty's Government and the other Governments concerned. His Majesty's Government will approach the problem in a sympathetic spirit and desire to make it clear at the outset that they welcome this French initiative to end the age-long feud with Germany and so bring unity and peace to Europe.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-d928cb23-c765-41d0-93ec-3b396b3a5449">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the Prime Minister consider giving an opportunity for Debate on this subject, if possible before we separate for Whitsuntide? It seems to be one on which the House should be entitled, not necessarily immediately, but after some consideration, to express its views and opinions.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-06b48afb-334d-4b98-ae30-2dab5f6273a2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
                Mr. Clement Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Before the Prime Minister replies, might I endorse what the right hon. Gentleman the Member for Woodford (Mr. Churchill) said, and say what I was about to say earlier? So often, these matters of vast public importance are Debated outside in the newspapers before the House has an opportunity of expressing its opinion. Therefore, will the Prime Minister provide the earliest opportunity for this House to discuss the matter?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-b3e0f6cb-d9e8-4c0a-ae5d-343edffb63e7">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think that probably it will be realised that it is a little early for me to give a definite reply at the moment. I should like to look into that very carefully. The matter should be discussed through the usual channels <span id="588" class="column-number" data-column-number="588"></span> to see just how things are going and how this matter can be arranged most conveniently for the House, and in the public interest.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-807096fc-e1de-422d-a2a9-ee81883019b1">
