        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7825f2f1-186f-4812-8f54-dd2e279d172c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-7825f2f1-186f-4812-8f54-dd2e279d172c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">With great respect, we feel very strongly that we should have the text before us. Of course, if it has been published in the newspapers we do not wish to press for the expense of printing a White Paper; but are we to have the full text before us or not?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7825f2f1-186f-4812-8f54-dd2e279d172c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-7825f2f1-186f-4812-8f54-dd2e279d172c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Yes, certainly, but this is a question of considering whether a statement which has, I understand, been put out very fully in the public Press, is necessarily to be circulated as a White Paper before it has been considered whether or not any comments, and the rest, should be put out with it. Sometimes, it may be a waste of time. I will certainly consider in what way we can assist the House best in this matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-26fc97e4-1743-48c5-886c-ac3145341562">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">With very great respect, we are entitled to the text. We are entitled to see what has been said. I really ask the Prime Minister to make sure that we get the text. Of course, if it has been given to the Press, we do not want to waste money on printing and paper; but, if not, we ought to have it as a Parliamentary Paper.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-05-11/debates/67f015bb-a27e-4f68-935d-1dd917a9640a/CoalAndSteelProduction(IntegrationProposals)#contribution-8e7dd2c0-c490-4f00-b09e-9c604173e34d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
